Interface TitanEdge

All Superinterfaces:
com.tinkerpop.blueprints.Edge, com.tinkerpop.blueprints.Element, TitanElement, TitanRelation, TitanVertex, com.tinkerpop.blueprints.Vertex
public interface TitanEdge
extends TitanRelation, com.tinkerpop.blueprints.Edge

A TitanEdge connects two TitanVertex. It extends the functionality provided by Blueprint's Edge.

Author:
Matthias Bröcheler (http://www.matthiasb.com)
